Hello everyone, this is Wang Gang

本期视频我跟大家分享一道家常菜
In this video, I'll introduce a home-cooking dish

鲍鱼汁蒸排骨
Baoyuzhi Zheng Paigu (Pork Rib Steamed with Abalone Sauce)

首先我们准备精瘦型的排骨 500 克
First, take 500g lean pork rib

将排骨头剁下来之后分成小段备用
Chop off the "head", and then chop it into smaller chunks

然后再将排骨分开之后剁成小段备用
Then divide the rib and chop it into short chunks

同学们精瘦型的排骨就是赘肉比较少的排骨
Note that "lean rib" means rib without much excessive meat

下一步开始处理排骨
Next, process the rib

首先在盆中加入适量的清水
First, add some water into the bowl

然后加入食用盐一小把抓洗五分钟
Add a handful of salt, and wash the rib for 5 minutes

排骨抓洗干净之后再放入清水中浸泡 60 分钟
After that, soak the rib in clean water for 60 minutes

这一步的目的是减少排骨中残留的血水
This is for reducing the remaining blood in the rib

下一步开始准备辅料
Next, prepare the Fu Liao ("auxiliary ingredients")

准备几根小葱头切碎放入碗中备用
Mince some green onion white and put it into a bowl

准备生姜一小块排散之后剁碎备用
Crush and mince a small piece of ginger

碗中加入鲍鱼汁 25 克
Add 25g abalone sauce into the bowl

加入胡椒粉半勺
Add half tsp of ground white pepper

加入少许白糖提鲜
Add a pinch of white sugar to bring out the umami flavor

加入生抽酱油 15 克
Add 15g light soy sauce

加入少许老抽调底色
Add a drizzle of dark soy sauce for coloring

再加入少许豆豉搅拌均匀备用
Also add a little douchi (aka. fermented black bean sauce)
And then mix up everything

排骨浸泡 60 分钟之后捞出挤干水分备用
After 60 minutes of soaking, take out the rib and squeeze out excess water

下一步开始调底味
Next, base seasoning

盆中加入少许食用盐
Add a pinch of salt into the bowl

加入鸡蛋清一个
Add a egg white

然后将排骨搅拌均匀
Then stir to mix up everything

排骨拌匀之后加入调好的鲍鱼汁
Then add in the seasoned abalone sauce

将排骨搅拌均匀腌制 60 分钟即可
Mix it up, and then marinate it for 60 minutes

同学们可以将排骨用此法腌制保存
Note that pork rib marinated in this way

然后放入冰箱现取现做
can be preserved refrigerated, and cooked when needed

准备冬瓜一小块
Take a small piece of winter melon

去籽之后切成薄片放入盘中垫底备用
Remove the seeds, then slice it and put it at the bottom of a plate

排骨上锅蒸之前再加入适量的土豆淀粉拌匀
Before steaming the pork rib, coat it with some potato starch

这样的目的是减少排骨的水分流失
This preserves the juiciness in the rib

排骨摆好之后下一步开始蒸制
Put the rib nicely in the plate. Next, steaming

将排骨放入蒸锅中开中火蒸 30 分钟
Steam the rib over medium heat for 30 minutes

同学们蒸制的时间需要根据排骨的老嫩做参考
Note that the steaming time depends on the tenderness of the pork

一般嫩排骨只需要蒸制 25 分钟即可脱骨
For tender pork, 25 minutes are enough to separate the meat from the bone

排骨蒸制 30 分钟之后取出撒上葱花即可上菜
30 minutes later, take out the rib and top it with some chopped green onion. Then it's ready to serve

一道老少皆宜的鲍鱼汁蒸排骨就制作完成
A Baoyuzhi Zheng Paigu (Pork Rib Steamed with Abalone Sauce) that fits everyone is thus complete!

下面开始蒸排骨的技术总结
Technical summary for steamed pork rib

第一，蒸排骨可以不用放油，这样可以保持清爽
1. For a refreshing taste, there's no need to add oil into steamed pork rib

第二，同学们最好选择精瘦型的排骨，排骨的肉太多反而不香
2. It's better to use lean pork rib. With too much meat, the dish is less flavorful

第三，排骨必须在上锅之前上淀粉，这样可以减少汁水的流失
3. The rib must be coated with starched before steaming, to preserve the juiciness

第四，蒸老排骨脱骨必须蒸制 40 分钟以上
4. For old rib, the steaming time is over 40 minutes

蒸排骨的技术总结完毕
That's all for the technical summary of steamed pork rib

